Name: MINIMUM SAFE DISTANCE 1 IN HUNDREDS OF METRES
Explanation: THE MINIMUM SAFE DISTANCE FOR WARNED, PROTECTED PERSONNEL EXPRESSED IN METRES TO THE NEAREST 100 METRES MEASURED FROM THE PLANNED GROUND ZERO.

Name: MINIMUM SAFE DISTANCE 2 IN HUNDREDS OF METRES
Explanation: THE MINIMUM SAFE DISTANCE FOR WARNED, EXPOSED PERSONNEL EXPRESSED IN METRES TO THE NEAREST 100 METRES MEASURED FROM THE PLANNED GROUND ZERO.
